<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Cricket" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Cricket,</orth> 1) an insect chirping about fireplaces: <bibl n="shak. shr 4.3.110" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 3, 110</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 1, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.100" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 100</bibl> <cit><quote>(as merry as --s)</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 1.4.63" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 4, 63</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.2.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 2, 16</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 2.2.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 2, 11</bibl>. Per. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.0." default="NO" valid="yes">III Prol. 7</bibl>.<lb />2) name of a fairy: <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.47" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. V, 5, 47</bibl>.
